snippet.title: Rev Heads Rally - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Meet the Rev Heads!

A group of thrill-seeking, hard-boiled, car crazy, adrenaline junkies determined to win the ‘Rev Heads Rally’ at all costs.
Each Rev Head brings their own style and charisma to the track as they go head-to-head in a battle for racing glory.

Join in the fun and compete in over 20 ‘Cup Series’ to collect additional Rev Heads and Vehicles – including an AR Race mode.


***Join the Spunge family!!***

Follow the team: http://www.twitter.com/SpungeGames
Become friends: http://www.facebook.com/SpungeGames
